Roadmap
-------

 - [webrtcgateway] Scalability using SIPThor
 - [webrtcgateway] Video bandwidth management
 - [webrtcgateway] SIP connect for multi-party video conference 
 - [webrtcgateway] Recording

Improvements
------------

 - change disabled_applications to active_applications which accepts a list
   which can contain the keyword ALL and [+/-]app_name tokens
 - debian package should rename config samples as .ini
 - for debian check if we can use the snakeoil cert from the ssl-cert package

